{"tid":290082,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人格甩底d汗有汗壓味","createTime":"2017-06-19T13:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T16:52:24.000Z","uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9032bd02c06dcaf387a9f870ed9f0d7a13781ca1","tid":290082,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:26:13.000Z","msg":"究境d汗壓味係點黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網google左都搵唔到，係汗嘅問題定係衫嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會係件衫著耐左又吸過好多汗，索左陣味入去洗唔甩，所以搞到一出汗陣味就出番後黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ddfd52e5a0518204261cb8d13b80a9b403019b","tid":290082,"uid":120051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:29:35.000Z","msg":"汗同尿嘅成份一樣架, 所以會壓壓臭臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但用碧X/ X蓮洗唔甩咩？"},{"pid":"20238b5abb4424878dde03ba45dfad1f8fc5a2de","tid":290082,"uid":14275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:30:07.000Z","msg":"濕熱"},{"pid":"803cd44a45f733126bb391c72bb19692099cf803","tid":290082,"uid":1858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T16:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>汗同尿嘅成份一樣架, 所以會壓壓臭臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但用碧X/ X蓮洗唔甩咩？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真嫁？<br />\n留明學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" cla